{"pid":"3c248ba645826df757185765231cfe973bc90be5","tid":575411,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a996cdac9338c68f940240a7b08505bdf36ca","tid":575411,"uid":69013,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"香港教學好少講228， 我前幾年去台灣旅行，識左台灣朋友，講起先知，我亦因此去左台北228紀念公園，亦睇左好多唔同角度既歷史。<br />\n<br />\n當時經日本統治過既台灣有「現代化」意識與建設，反而從中國大陸戰敗過來既國民軍無接受過「現代化」，初到步根本係能力無知識去管治，不同習慣不同文代造成好大矛盾，無釋出壓力反而高壓管治，最後爆出228事件。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"228 係1947年發生 當時既國民黨都仲同共產黨打緊平手 點樣係戰敗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86ea969f5f6ae60166f18bc11d13d9c2ea3f1fc","tid":575411,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c71e426156e63d959560b622aef0d8a4e6793fc0","tid":575411,"uid":33359,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"最仆街就係果個陳儀<br />\n一邊話談判,另一邊就同老蔣講話D台灣人係共產黨派黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"陳儀最後投共比人打左把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c99785a9b4dff4c459aa7bc8e93b62d7c47986c","tid":575411,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"信一半"},{"pid":"34973b29684222b1e865aa06db4bbf303261c468","tid":575411,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9826b924c0ad227197e34aeebfc94fdd4534a13","tid":575411,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c248ba645826df757185765231cfe973bc90be5","tid":575411,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a996cdac9338c68f940240a7b08505bdf36ca","tid":575411,"uid":69013,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:3