社成員陳俞璋說，<br />\n<br />\n執政當局在《促進轉型正義條例》通過後，應徹底清除威權遺緒、廢除兩蔣文化園區。不過，現場也發生插曲，一名自稱《中時》記者的男子提問時，與獨派青年發生口角，雙方演變為推擠衝突，最後該男在叫罵聲下自行離去。"},{"pid":"8ae0f21f57e3a8acc54ebe807276fa01423fd13a","tid":575411,"uid":53705,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"諗起D  中華膠 成日稱 蔣介石做 蔣公, 蔣委員會 就覺得好笑<br />\n<br />\n條友根本係 失敗版既毛澤東"},{"pid":"1acc23508bafbd952e1bbf5d1dcaad30936f4ff7","tid":575411,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"蔣匪係支那大陸打真共匪又唔見佢咁勇"},{"pid":"3c0498035fcafc922b3253ad33dca541f65084c7","tid":575411,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ff2b40424989aa7f8bb1229eb496e2f4a8b5ee4","tid":575411,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"睇過度另一版本，係由買煙引起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"成單野就好似香港場魚革咁"},{"pid":"fe9bac6df6edb81ddffb782c20e91bc811f858b4","tid":575411,"uid":163350,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d3e26966392b5be8ed283db435535af27033526","tid":575411,"uid":40216,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"通州屠殺日本人，228屠殺台灣人，之後日日扮南京大屠殺受害者"},{"pid":"f028b25f3af5448bdc577f1e446a3fbf645dc510","tid":575411,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9263e205e6b7e0be5db4c8ac19cde82e3f2026f1","tid":575411,"uid":35790,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"諗起孫中山聯俄聯共建立黃埔軍校<br />\n武力震壓廣州商團事件"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"係聯俄容共，聯俄聯共係共產黨叫法"},{"pid":"f52aa600def1bb0788c3866cbbb2bd6c0db7b75a","tid":575411,"uid":22378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe9bac6df6edb81ddffb782c20e91bc811f858b4","tid":575411,"uid":163350,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8ae0f21f57e3a8acc54ebe807276fa01423fd13a","tid":575411,"uid":53705,"like":12,"dislike