https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2016-03-03%2F70708&d=%2BPRhXb9zV22wmtLrXLVMU8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c2c51e15\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2016-03-03/70708</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"83dbd6adede5cebfc92db35d9af6ac39013fcbc6","tid":575411,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"51d02b7f88ebb0bb5cb2aaeee6688d5ebdc57383","tid":575411,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ec5fda073af53c8e4c02b3d6a62bcb747a5ff835","tid":575411,"uid":45914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"75f510772db4ca01a34e9096440dddea2bd35a4f","tid":575411,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:47:09.000Z","msg":"起碼蔣先生仲會講兩句禮義廉恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"老蔣屠殺，屠咗邊啲殺咗邊個先？如果你講二二八民軍，咁係佢哋革命戰爭失敗，邊有搶完軍火、圍攻過官署、接管過政權然後人哋援軍一登陸即刻變返做無罪良民咁過抵玩嘅道理？<br />\n<br />\n「二二八事件」根本唔止係一個「事件」，而係一場戰役，由台灣民軍對抗國民革命軍。難道你以為二二八就只係國軍坐喺大卡車沿街掃射無辜民眾咁簡單？定還是你以為當時嘅台灣民眾好似雨傘咁手無寸鐵、好似年初一咁剩係得竹同磚頭？佢哋真係「要槍有槍，要炮有炮」㗎。建議大家睇多啲檔案同專書，就算你讀獨派史書都可以。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 台中民兵「二七部隊」有兩個指揮官到依家都未死，佢哋係親自承認當時自己手下民兵有長槍過千枝、手榴彈兩萬粒。<br />\n<blockquote>當年的部隊長鍾逸人表示，軍火主要來自接收的營區、警局，長槍約有千餘支，手榴彈有2千箱（1箱10顆，共2萬餘顆）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2016-03-03/70708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2016-03-03%2F70708&d=%2BPRhXb9zV22wmtLrXLVMU8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c2c51e15\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2016-03-03/70708</a></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"講多句，二七部隊最大粒嗰個叫謝雪紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/001552_1aabc30f2b0b9bb49532e23c93bd3080.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.ne